                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SCHLIX CMS v2.1.7 (build #1) has been released today. The base theme has been changed to dark by default, inspired by KDE's Dark Breeze and Ubuntu's Unity theme. The light theme will still be available as a separate download at the end of December 2017 (or maybe January 2018) and you can customize it with your company logo. This will be useful for web design agencies and freelancers out there. In addition to this, there is already a custom admin theme that you can download from the &lt;a href="https://www.schlix.com/extensions/themes/"&gt;Themes&lt;/a&gt; directory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Other important changes:&lt;/p&gt;
