&lt;li&gt;Enhancement: Contact form is now using fully AJAX so it can be inserted in the middle of the content.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;New InsertContactForm macro to embed contact form in the middle of any content text&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
